snippet.title: Tyranids revealed in new demo for Warhammer SKULLS!
snippet.description:
The Tyranids are here! Hive Fleet Leviathan besieges the galaxy, getting ready to devour all as the final one of the starting armies of Warhammer 40.000: Warpforge! Take a look at the new faction in the latest web post:
https://www.warpforge40k.com/warhammer-skulls-2023-demo/

To celebrate the Warhammer SKULLS festival, Warpforge receives a new demo in which you will be able to play with the new Tyranids army for the first time. Prepare for an onslaught of horrors, scythe-limbed aliens and broods of ferocious beasts, as Leviathan Hive Fleet swarms into battle!

Play on Steam now, only until 1st June, and join the community on social media!
Steam ► https://store.steampowered.com/app/1985170/Warhammer_40000_Warpforge/
Discord ► https://www.discord.gg/warpforge
Twitter ► https://twitter.com/warpforge40k
Instagram ► https://www.instagram.com/warpforge40k/
